entities.name: ElizaOS
entities.description: An AI agent platform focused on composability and extensibility through its plugin ecosystem. It aims to provide infrastructure for building and monetizing AI agents.

entities.name: GitHub
entities.description: A web-based platform for version control and collaboration using Git. It allows developers to host and manage code repositories, track changes, and work together on software development projects.

entities.name: Auto.fun
entities.description: An infrastructure platform designed for launching AI agents, tokens, and coordination mechanisms without requiring users to write code. It focuses on agent monetization and has a marketing strategy involving 'eli5' and token launches.

entities.name: OpenAI
entities.description: A research and deployment company focused on artificial intelligence. Known for developing models like ChatGPT and for its products and services related to AI.

entities.name: ChatGPT
entities.description: A large language model developed by OpenAI, designed for conversational interactions. It aims to remember user conversations to provide personalized responses.

entities.name: ElevenLabs
entities.description: A company that provides advanced AI-powered voice synthesis technology. They offer text-to-speech and voice cloning services.

entities.name: YouTube
entities.description: An online video-sharing platform where users can upload, view, and share videos. It is also used for content creation and monetization.

entities.name: OpenRouter
entities.description: A service that provides an API gateway for accessing various large language models. It aims to offer a unified interface but has limitations such as lacking embedding support in certain integrations.
